\uc0\u10022  Understanding:\
  I understand you want to temporarily disable the voice and file upload features in the chat interface.\
  You also want to add the ability to right-click a message to open an inline context menu where users can directly edit the text and press enter to save, or delete the message, causing the remaining\
  messages to smoothly slide into the newly empty space.\
\
  Implementation:\
  Yes, this is entirely possible and a great UX pattern.\
  I will implement this by adding PATCH and DELETE endpoints to the backend API, and then building a custom React right-click context menu in the frontend that handles inline state editing and uses CSS\
  transitions (like Framer Motion or Tailwind animate) for the smooth deletion repositioning.\
